        <!-- Section INTRODUCTION -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
            <p>Sales management is one of the fundamental pillars of a company's commercial performance. With Movelys, this function is fully digitized and optimized through a powerful, intuitive, and interconnected module. Designed to meet the needs of businesses of all sizes, this module allows real-time tracking of every sales transaction, from order registration to final payment.</p>
            
            <p>The application provides a fluid interface for creating invoices, adding sold products or services, applying discounts, taxes, managing partial or complete payments, as well as precise customer tracking. Every operation is recorded rigorously, ensuring complete traceability and transparency at all stages of the sales cycle.</p>
            
            <p>Movelys also enables in-depth analysis of commercial activity through detailed reports, offering a global view of performance, margins, most active customers, and best-selling products. By linking sales management with inventory, contacts, and finance modules, Movelys provides a unified view essential for strategic decision-making.</p>
        </section>

