            <h2 id="all-sales">1) All sales</h2>
            
            <h3 id="general-function">1.1) General function</h3>
            <p>The <strong>All sales</strong> section constitutes the <strong>central dashboard for commercial management</strong> in Movelys. It groups all sales made in the system, whether direct sales, point of sale (POS) transactions, converted quotes, or orders recorded through other channels (import, drafts, returns, etc.).</p>
            <p>It enables <strong>precise, fast, and organized tracking of each customer transaction</strong>, from initial registration to complete payment and delivery.</p>
            
            <h3 id="interface-tools">1.2) Interface and available tools</h3>
            <p>The interface of this section is based on a <strong>dynamic, filterable, and customizable table</strong>, equipped with several processing functions.</p>
            
            <h4>Available functions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Entries per page: Allows displaying 10, 25, 50, or 100 sales per screen</li>
                <li><strong>Quick search:</strong> Search bar filtering results instantly (by customer, sale number, status, etc.)</li>
                <li><strong>CSV/Excel export:</strong> Allows downloading data for external use</li>
                <li><strong>Print:</strong> Generates a printable version of the list</li>
                <li><strong>Column visibility:</strong> Allows showing/hiding certain fields</li>
                <li><strong>Add a sale:</strong> Direct access to the form for creating a new sale</li>
            </ul>
            
