            <h2 id="pos">4) Pos</h2>
            
            <h3 id="pos-interface-objective">4.1) Functionality objective & interface</h3>
            <p>The POS (Point Of Sale) form in Movelys allows quick and complete entry of a <strong>physical in-store sale.</strong> It is designed to optimize the work of cashiers or sellers at a physical point of sale by providing an interface that is:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Intuitive and ergonomic,</strong></li>
                <li>Capable of handling complex transactions (discounts, deliveries, taxes),</li>
                <li>And directly integrated with inventory, customer, and cash register management.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The objective is to enable:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Direct sale of in-stock products,</li>
                <li>Quick payment collection,</li>
                <li>Generation of customer receipts,</li>
                <li>Tracking of POS transactions.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="image-placeholder">
