            <ul>
                <li><strong>Orders pending validation,</strong></li>
                <li>Sales <strong>partially paid or to be confirmed,</strong></li>
                <li>Or order preparations in a multi-step process.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3 id="draft-objectives">5.2) Functionality objectives</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Allow <strong>flexibility in managing incomplete sales.</strong></li>
                <li>Provide a temporary workspace before final confirmation.</li>
                <li>Help <strong>coordination between sales and accounting teams.</strong></li>
                <li>Reduce errors by taking time to <strong>verify information before finalization.</strong></li>
            </ul>
            
