                <li>Pending delivery,</li>
                <li>In transit,</li>
                <li>Delivered,</li>
                <li>Cancelled.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This status evolves with logistics tracking. It is crucial for customer service, traceability, and reminders.</p>
            
