            <h5>6. Delivery person</h5>
            <p>Name or identifier of the person in charge of order delivery. It can be:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>An internal employee (logistics),</li>
                <li>A partner carrier,</li>
                <li>Or an external company</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This field facilitates responsibility tracking and potential claims.</p>
            
            <h5>7. Shipping documents</h5>
            <p>Files related to delivery: delivery note (DN), carrier slip, proof of receipt, etc. Accepted formats: PDF, images, Excel, Word...</p>
