            <h5>Button: Add additional expenses</h5>
            <p>This button allows recording <strong>expenses associated with the order but not billed to the customer.</strong> Expense examples:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Packaging costs,</li>
                <li>Handling,</li>
                <li>Transport commission,</li>
                <li>Purchase of shipping-related accessories.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h5>What is it for?</h5>
            <ul>
                <li>To track the real profitability of the order,</li>
                <li>Allocate these costs in analytical accounting,</li>
                <li>Manage a journal of logistics expenses per sale.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These expenses don't impact the customer total but enrich <strong>internal</strong> cost reports.</p>
            
